Title: God, I'm Tired
Writer: Luke Jennings (based on the Villanelle novels by), Phoebe Waller-Bridge
Actors: David Bertrand, Jodie Comer, Yuli Lagodinsky, Sean Delaney
Plot: Eve and Kenny confront Carolyn, but get a surprise that leads them deeper into the conspiracy. Villanelle goes on the run with a hostage that might be more than she can handle.
